{"tid":746417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【睇見想嘔】乾碗機3年飄屍臭 拆開驚見百隻曱甴屍","createTime":"2018-07-17T13:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T01:01:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a9d157459fa242ac6e0aa4a61abcad48182c2e4e","tid":746417,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"台灣雲林婦人呂蕙宇3年前換購櫻花牌廚具，豈料半年後，廚房散發出臭味，尤其使用乾碗機時更明顯，拆開廚具才發現，底層空隙竟有上百隻死曱甴，質疑是施工未密封排水孔縫隙，而讓曱甴鑽入。櫻花職員指出：「我們只賣廚具！」只願換新廚具，拒絕補償長期聞臭味之害。<br />\n<br />\n呂蕙宇於2014年底購買虎尾鎮單位，入伙後再換購櫻花廚具。後來發現不斷傳出臭味，而且集中乾碗機出風口，遂職員上門檢測，發現機器運作正常，懷疑裏有死動物。呂蕙宇後來折開乾碗機，發現內裏有近百隻曱甴屍體。<br />\n<br />\n呂蕙宇懷疑曱甴從乾碗機爬入廚具，加上乾碗機散出熱氣，等於乾碗烤蟑螂，然而向生產商投訴，卻未重視，甚至認為問題源於施工問題，並非廚具引起。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的櫻花公司企劃處總監鄧淑貞表示，呂小姐本月6日向公司反映問題，公司已處理，確認客人滿意才會結案，資料上，公司已多次聯繫呂小姐，且周日派員至呂家了解，不知呂小姐不滿意協商結果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/215407_5f73d2d8fcde8f4ebc36fe572856bc27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F215407_5f73d2d8fcde8f4ebc36fe572856bc27.png&h=372e37e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180717/58452111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F58452111&d=eGzFkpZEALB1PzcJy8m%2FKxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=8ed0bf54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F58452111&h=fe6f65ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180717/58452111</a>"},{"pid":"3d3061be7743ea61c7df810e0658735920c7b2c4","tid":746417,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:56:51.000Z","msg":"其實關部機設計咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb9d48976557a73ad25217f539b27c6136a8af0","tid":746417,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:57:45.000Z","msg":"磨粉沖水飲，大量蛋白質，有益身心"},{"pid":"2d38c73c0f87eb06356b86dc29670645fe0dae93","tid":746417,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:01:52.000Z","msg":"小強乾"},{"pid":"babbb96b80701eec00530e875fc322588b5fdf81","tid":746417,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:08:26.000Z","msg":"殺曱甴神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果無乾碗機殺曱甴，屋企有幾百隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5a3c39f172a5a2474d638a7bb2ffed92fbaf6c","tid":746417,"uid":124107,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dad045f2f32aefaa74fed4bdf05c8d2b65c281ab","tid":746417,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:26:07.000Z","msg":"不嬲焗爐同洗碗機都好拿渣"},{"pid":"0766b6706267a2c3fc6e65da310983f2deaf9f76","tid":746417,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T01:01:24.000Z","msg":"推post"}]}